    Fix stepd segfault when using proctrack/linux
    
    This appears to be an oversight of 865338c7f33 where the cont_id check
    was changed from NO_VAL64 to INFINITE64. The cont_id is initialized to
    NO_VAL64 in src/common/slurm_jobacct_gather.c.

